EN: The tree-lined path reverberated with echoes.

ZH: 夜晚的回音特别嘹亮。
EN: The echoes at night are especially loud.

ZH: 孩子们很喜欢在空旷的场地上制造回音。
EN: Children love to make echoes in open spaces.

ZH: 对着墙壁呼唤你的名字，就能听到回音。
EN: Call out your name against the wall, and you'll hear the echoes.

ZH: 我们漫步在湖边，听着湖水激起的回音。
EN: We walked by the lake, listening to the echoes of the water.

